title: Kennedy.2015.08.26.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

Kennedy kicks the night off talking about the hill that Republican's have chosen to die on. Trump showed that his anti-immigration talk is popular and many GOP candidates are following his lead.

On the panel we've got BEN KISSEL, BRIAN MORGANSTERN, and KAYLEIGH MCENANY. They continue to talk about Trump, the GOP, and immigration. Next - Hillary cuts her vacation, is reportedly very agitated about a potential Biden bid.

DANA PERINO is in studio to talk about the Press Do's and Don'ts for 2016 candidates. 1. Get to know the reporters. 2. Respect the role of the press. 3. Read what the press writes. 4. Don't wall yourself off from the press.

The panel returns to talk about Curt Shilling's recent tweet comparing Islam to Nazis and ESPN's response.

Fact or Fiction: The Ben Carson edition. The panel is back to answer a series of true or false questions about presidential candidate Ben Carson.

Air Jaws: Walking With Great Whites has set records for Discovery. The natural history producer JEFF KURR is here via satellite to discuss it.

Nightcap: Costume Controversy.
